text: Any Wednesday is a 1966 American romantic comedy movie directed by first time director Robert Ellis Miller and starring Jane Fonda, Jason Robards, Dean Jones, Rosemary Murphy, Ann Prentiss. It was distributed by Warner Bros. and was based on the play of the same name. ==Other websites== * * * Category:1966 romantic comedy movies Category:American romantic comedy movies Category:Movies based on plays Category:Warner Bros. movies
title: Any Wednesday
